description.en-US:
📖📖📖    Tabs Counter extension/add-on aims to provide an instants calculation of the number of open tabs in the web browser via a clean and intuitive interface. Tabs Counter might be useful for software engineers, product managers, marketing teams who do a lot of research. Also, it is a very useful tool to anyone who usually has tens of tabs opened at the same time. Tabs Counter is a simple and useful cross web-browser compatible extension/addon that lets you get in real time the number of opened tabs in your web browser.


🎨🎨🎨    Tabs Counter Version 0.1.0 - Web Browser Extension/Add-on Features:
✅ Displays the count of open tabs in the currently active open window of the web browser
✅ No permissions or requirements are needed
✅ To enable in incognito mode, turn on 'Allow in incognito' from web browser setting


🎨🎨🎨    Tabs Counter Next Version Features:
✅ Displays number of open tabs in the current active window or across all open windows of the browser
✅ Displays number of browser open windows
✅ Ability to change the icon background color
✅ Ability to add a numeric prefix before the tab's title (e.g. "2. YouTube")
✅ Detect duplicate tabs in the current active window or across all open windows of the browser
📖📖📖  Duplicate tabs are tabs with the same exact URL
📖📖📖  Adds a special icon before the duplicate tab name
📖📖📖  Close all duplicate tabs instances retaining one with a single click only
✅ Detect stale tabs which has been opened for X days. Auto close of staled tabs based on your configuration in the settings

📝📝📝    Like or love it? Please leave us a review

ℹ️ℹ️ℹ️    Support Email: support@oziku.tech
✅ All translations are done with a translator. For any wrong translation please reach out to us
✅ For any bugs found or feature request please do not hesitate to send us an email
